arch sign
name One Drop Quests (non trigger quests)
msg
"one drop" and "special drop" quests.
These "quests" don't need a going quest and/or
a trigger. They will "self appear" when the player
does a defined action - like kill a special mob or
open a special container.
endmsg
x 2
y 1
end
